      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Lucita$<BR>Ah, he-hello. <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>...<BR>Erm, er... If you're not busy, could you listen to me for a while?</html>]]></talk_question>
