      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Lucita$<BR>A-actually, there's a used item that Pedro left in our shop that kind of b-bothers me...<BR>my master said that it's just rubbish so I should burn it, but I sneaked it out and kept it somewhere.<BR>
If it's ok with you, could you take a look?</html>]]></talk_question>
