      <talk_question mid="63"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tamara${action:Talk}<BR>Can't be~ Karacule doesn't have any frie... Ehem!<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Tamara feigns a cough and tries to cover up)</FONT><BR>...If you read the letter, it says that the person will come and see her on the way from Saint Haven to somewhere.</html>]]></talk_question>
